    "Autoencoders (AEs)In that they are an adaptation of FFNNs rather than a fundamentally unique design, autoencoders (AEs) are similar to FFNNs in this regard.",
    "The only thing to keep in mind is that the number of input characteristics (number of neurons) in the input layer and the output layer should match (the number of neurons).",
    "Check to see if the input and output are both equal.",
    "The basic idea behind autoencoders is to automatically compress data rather than encrypt it, hence the name.",
